Title: 65. Unexpected reinforcements
Text:
Dwarves are here?
And they are fighting the undead!
I must deliver the message to Captain!
Captain is currently besieging Northast.

pages: {"text":"Observing group number 7.\n\nMy companion have returned from Northast. Large amount of undead soldiers have left Lost city and attacked Northast with destructible force."}

{"text":"We are curently hidden in the catacombs of old watching tower.\n\nFrom observing group number 12 we found out that Undead have sealed entrance to the Lost city, so there is no possible way to reach it from neither side now."}
{"text":"Human army just disembarked near Aerilon. It must be reaction to the attack that happened few days before."}
{"text":"We can not leave the tower, for undead took it for their own!\n\nIt is just a matter of time before they decide to check the basement completely!"}
